“疫情”中的安徽马鞍山：医院设发热门诊分诊处、口罩脱销、景点暂停开放。
"Outbreak" in Anhui Ma On Shan: the hospital set up a fever clinic, mask sales, scenic spots temporarily open.
作者：夏治斌 石英婧 来源：中国经营网。
Author: Xia Zhibin Quartz Jing Jing: China Business Network.
本报记者 夏治斌 石英婧 马鞍山 上海报道“今天早上看到（马鞍山）有确诊病例，我们就在家人群里跟所有亲戚都说今年就不拜年不走动了，等熬过这个特殊时期大家再聚，我觉得每个人把自己保护好了就是在给社会做贡献了。
Our reporter Xia Zhibin quartz reported in Shanghai that there was a confirmed case of Jing in Ma On Shan this morning. We told all our relatives that we would not visit the New Year or walk around.
”1月25日，即鼠年大年初一，安徽马鞍山人夏安（化名）向《中国经营报》记者如上说道。
On January 25, the first day of the Year of the Rat, Xia An (alias) of Ma On Shan, Anhui Province, told China Business Daily.
按照往年的习惯，每年的大年初一，夏安就会开始走亲访友，但今年新型冠状病毒疫情还在肆虐，“疫情阴霾”之下，记者身边包括夏安在内的众多亲朋好友，都认识到情况的严峻性，尽量减少不必要外出的频次，即便是出门大部分人也佩戴了口罩。
In accordance with the custom of previous years, each year on the New Year's Day, Xia An will start to visit friends and relatives, but this year, the new coronavirus epidemic is still raging. Under the "shadow of the epidemic," many friends and relatives, including Xia An, are aware of the seriousness of the situation.
一位当涂县乌溪镇的电信工作人员王宇（化名）告诉记者，考虑到现在的疫情现状，大家的卫生意识都提高了，公司也要求大家出去做安装宽带等业务，都必须佩戴口罩。
Wang Yu (not his real name), a telecommunications worker in Wuxi Township in Dangdu County, told reporters that given the current situation, health awareness has increased and companies are asking everyone to go out to install broadband and other businesses and wear masks.
“戴口罩既能让自己心安，也能让客户放心。
Wearing a mask reassures both the customer and the client.
”1月25日，当涂县乌溪镇的电信工作人员王宇佩戴口罩外出工作（受访者提供）自武汉市卫健委2019年12月31日首次公告发现不明肺炎病例至今，已经整整过去了25天。
On January 25, it has been 25 days since the first announcement by Wuhan Health Commission on December 31, 2019 that an unidentified pneumonia case had been discovered when Wang Yu, a telecommunications worker in Wuxi township of Tou county, went out to work wearing a mask.
安徽省卫健委消息显示，1月24日0～24时，安徽省新增报告新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎确诊病例24例。
On January 24, 0-24, 24 new cases of confirmed pneumonia with a new coronavirus infection were reported in Anhui Province, according to the Health Commission of Anhui Province.
其中合肥市4例、铜陵市3例、安庆市3例、马鞍山市4例、阜阳市5例、亳州市3例、芜湖市1例、滁州市1例。
There were 4 cases in Hefei City, 3 cases in Tongling City, 3 cases in Anqing City, 4 cases in Maanshan City, 5 cases in Fuyang City, 3 cases in Bozhou City, 1 case in Wuhu City and 1 case in Chuzhou City.
铜陵市、马鞍山市、芜湖市为首次病例报告。
The first cases were reported in Tongling City, Ma On Shan City and Wuhu City.
在新增的24例确诊病例中，22例有武汉居住史和旅行史，2例为聚集性传播病例。
Of the 24 newly diagnosed cases, 22 had Wuhan residence history and travel history, and 2 had concentrated cases of sexually transmitted diseases.
部分药店口罩脱销1月25日，记者来到当涂街道上的多家药店，多位药店工作人员称，店内的所有口罩早在三四天前便已脱销。
Some drug stores have been out of business for three or four days, according to drugstore workers who visited a number of pharmacies on the streets on January 25.
由于现在是过年期间，物流不通，因此目前店内口罩暂时没法供应。
As it is the New Year period, logistics is not available, so the current supply of in-store masks is not available.
随后，记者来到马鞍山当涂东站，只见在候车大厅大屏幕在实时播放新型冠状病毒的情况。
Subsequently, the reporter came to Ma On Shan when Tu Tu station, only to see in the waiting hall in real-time broadcast of the new coronavirus situation.
现场的检票员，包括车站的安保人员、乘客均佩戴口罩。
At the scene of the ticket inspectors, including station security personnel, passengers are wearing masks.
1月25日，当涂东站候车厅内大屏幕播放如何正确戴口罩。
On January 25, a large screen in the waiting area of Tu Tung Station shows how to wear a mask properly.
夏治斌/摄影与此同时，记者来到当涂县人民医院综合病房大楼一楼，一进大厅，便可看见发热门诊预检分诊处，室内人员同样都佩戴口罩，现场有医生人员在给患者测量体温。
Xia Zhibin / Photography At the same time, the reporter came to Dangtuo County People's Hospital General Ward Building, a hall, you can see the fever clinic, indoor staff are also wearing masks, the scene of a doctor to take temperature.
据医院内一位工作人员介绍，上述分诊处是最近四五天设置的，主要就是为了筛查发热病人。
The clinic was set up four or five days ago to screen febrile patients, according to a hospital staff member.
1月25日，当涂县人民医院医务人员在给患者测体温。
On January 25, medical staff at Tu County People's Hospital took the patient's temperature.
夏治斌/摄影医院内摆放的发热病人就诊流程显示，如若就诊患者发热，护士会赠送外科口罩，并前往发热门诊就诊。
The process of treating febrile patients in Xia Zhibin / Photography Hospital shows that if the patient is febrile, the nurse will give away the surgical mask and go to the fever clinic.
如进一步诊断显示疑似人感染新型冠状病毒肺炎则就要佩戴N95口罩，再进入发热病人隔离病房，进行隔离、查体、流调，做好个人防护。
If further diagnosis shows that a person is suspected to be infected with the new coronavirus pneumonia, he should wear a N95 mask and enter the isolation ward of the fever patient for isolation.
此外，在就诊示意图旁边还有一则提示，要求近期从武汉回来或者和武汉回来人员有接触史者需要主动告知医护人员。
In addition, next to the chart there is a reminder that people who have recently returned from Wuhan or have contact with those who have returned to Wuhan need to voluntarily inform the medical staff.
当涂县人民医院发热门诊医护人员穿戴有防护服坐诊。
When Tu county people's hospital febrile out-patient medical personnel wear protective clothing sit-in.
夏治斌/摄影记者现场跟随指示牌来到位于感染科的发热门诊处，在发热门诊的医生均穿戴防护服。
Xia Zhibin / Photographer followed the signs to the fever clinic in the Infection Department and all the doctors at the fever clinic wore protective clothing.
一位工作人员告诉记者，现在的发热门诊是最近新设的。
A staff member told reporters that the current fever clinic is newly established.
记者获取的一份马鞍山市卫健委文件显示，马鞍山市第四人民医院（即马鞍山市传染病医院）为市级定点医院。
The reporter obtained a document of Ma Anshan city health committee showed that the fourth people's hospital in Anshan City (that is, Ma On Shan infectious disease hospital) for city hospitals.
该医院的一位工作人员向记者表示：“如果是马鞍山确诊的病例，基本上都会送到这里来收治。
"If it's a confirmed case in Ma On Shan, it's basically going to be there," a hospital worker told reporters.
”另有一位马鞍山市医护人员告诉记者，其所在医院的发热门诊医护人员全部取消了春节假期，都在工作。
A paramedic at Ma On Shan also told reporters that all his hospital's fever clinic staff had canceled their Spring Festival holidays and were at work.
多家景点暂停对外开放记者了解到，1月23日深夜，安徽省卫生健康委便发出了《动员令》，宣布全省卫生健康系统取消2020年春节放假。
Many scenic spots have suspended opening to the outside world Reporters learned that late on January 23, Anhui Province, the Health and Health Commission issued a "mobilization order," announced the province's health health system to cancel the 2020 Spring Festival holiday.
各市、县卫生健康委、医疗卫生机构以及疾控中心在春节期间将照常上班。
The city and county health committees, medical and health institutions and the CDC will work as usual during the Spring Festival.
1月24日，根据《安徽省突发公共卫生事件应急预案》《安徽省新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控应急预案》，结合安徽省当前新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控形势，安徽省新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控应急指挥部决定，启动安徽省重大公共卫生事件一级响应。
On January 24, according to the Emergency Plan for Public Health Emergencies in Anhui Province and the Emergency Plan for the Prevention and Control of Pneumonia Infected by the New Coronavirus Infection in Anhui Province, the Emergency Command of Pneumonia Prevention and Control of the New Coronavirus Infection in Anhui Province decided to activate the first-level response to major public health events in Anhui Province.
与此同时，安徽省教育厅对全省教育系统做好新型冠状病毒感染的肺炎疫情防控工作作出部署：寒假期间，各地各高校要对留校学生发布预警提醒，非必要原因不外出，尤其不到人流量大的场所逗留；严格控制外来人员随意进入校园，取消各种旅游团组进入校园。
At the same time, Anhui Provincial Education Bureau has made arrangements for the prevention and control of pneumonia caused by the new coronavirus infection in the province's education system.During the winter vacation, colleges and universities throughout the province should issue early-warning warnings to students staying in schools, not to go out for unnecessary reasons, especially in places with large traffic.
各地各校要提前对春季开学有关情况做出科学研判，必要时对学校教学安排及相关工作做出调整。
Schools everywhere should make scientific assessment of the situation in advance of the start of the spring school, and make adjustments to the school's teaching arrangements and related work when necessary.
为应对疫情，马鞍山市也采取了一系列的防控措施，采石矶景区从2020年1月25日起暂停对外开放，具体开放时间另行通知。
In response to the outbreak, Ma On Shan City has also taken a series of measures to prevent and control the stone scenic spots from January 25, 2020 from the opening date to be announced.
当涂县李白墓园暂停对外开放，具体开放时间待定（原定大年初五免费开放也同时取消）。
The opening hours of Li Bai cemetery in Tu County will be suspended until the beginning of the year.
除此之外，春节放假期间（除夕~正月初六）马鞍山市雨山区小九华寺、含山县褒禅寺、太湖禅寺、和县凤林禅寺、当涂县甑山禅林、花山区临溪寺等佛教场所暂停对外开放，外来人员禁止进入寺院。
In addition, during the Spring Festival holiday (New Year's Eve ~ early January 6), Ma On Shan small Jiuhua Temple, Baochang Temple, Taihu Lake Zen Temple, and County Fenglin Zen Temple, Dangtuo County retort Mountain Zen Forest, Huashan Mountain Linxi Temple are temporarily closed to the outside world.
另在2020年1月11日后来自武汉以及途经武汉至马鞍山市的所有人员，应当到村、社区进行登记。
In addition, all personnel coming from Wuhan and passing through Wuhan to Ma On Shan City after January 11, 2020 shall register in the villages and communities.
自觉在家自我观察不少于14天；如有发热、呼吸道感染症状的，应立即前往就近的二级以上医疗机构发热门诊规范治疗。
Self-observation at home no less than 14 days; if there is fever, respiratory tract infection symptoms, should immediately go to the nearest health-care facilities above level II fever clinic standard treatment.
（编辑：石英婧 校对：彭玉凤）。
